Chat Application with Real-time Messaging and Chatbot

Overview

This is a real-time chat application that allows users to sign up, log in, join chat rooms, send private messages, and interact with a chatbot. It uses Socket.io for real-time communication and MongoDB for message persistence.

Features

User Authentication: Signup & Login with hashed passwords.

Chat Rooms: Users can join, chat, and leave rooms.

Private Messaging: One-to-one messaging with real-time updates.

Typing Indicator: Displays when a user is typing.

Chatbot: Provides automated responses based on user queries.

MongoDB Storage: Stores messages, user details, and chatbot interactions.

User Management: Admins can add/remove users from rooms.

Logout Confirmation: Prevents accidental logouts.

Technologies Used

Frontend: HTML, CSS (Tailwind, Bootstrap), JavaScript, jQuery

Backend: Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, Mongoose

Real-time Communication: Socket.io

Authentication: JWT (JSON Web Token) with bcrypt password hashing

Installation & Setup

1. Clone the Repository

 git clone https://github.com/your-repo/chat-app.git
 cd chat-app

2. Install Dependencies

 npm install

3. Configure Environment Variables

Create a .env file and add:

MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
PORT=3000

4. Start the Server

 npm run dev

5. Open the Chat App

Go to http://localhost:3000 in your browser.

API Endpoints

Authentication

POST /auth/signup - Register a new user

POST /auth/login - Authenticate a user

Chat Functionality

POST /chat/group-message - Send a group message

POST /chat/private-message - Send a private message

GET /chat/group-history/:room - Get chat history for a room

GET /chat/private-history/:from_user/:to_user - Get private messages

WebSocket Events

joinRoom: User joins a chat room

sendMessage: Send a message to a room

leaveRoom: User leaves a chat room

typing: Displays a typing indicator

privateMessage: Sends a private message

Future Enhancements

User Profiles with avatars

File Sharing within chat rooms

Better UI Design with animations

